text: Laura Jones may refer to: *Laura Jones (gymnast) (born 1992), British gymnast *Laura Jones (journalist) (born 1975), British television journalist *Laura Jones (screenwriter) (born 1951), Australian screenwriter *Laura Jones (soccer) (born 1969), American soccer player *Laura Anne Jones (born 1979), former member of the National Assembly for Wales *Laura Jones (Fraser Institute), Canadian economist and policy analyst *Laura Jones (politician), American politician, member of the New Hampshire House of Representatives *Laura Jones (born 1960), American singer, better known by her stage name Laura Love
